title: Furnished Corner Studio At A Great Rate!!
posting_body: ['This fully furnished studio apartment features new flooring and large windows bringing in abundant natural light; full-size kitchen with cooking accessories, dishwasher, microwave, and a full-size refrigerator.', '3D Tour of similar apartment: <URL>', 'Other highlights and benefits of this fully furnished apartment include a walk-in closet with an abundance of storage space, queen-size bed with linens, towels, nightstands, TV with media unit, dining set, sofa, chair with ottoman, side tables, and more!', "Located in Pacific Heights; One of San Francisco's most prestigious neighborhoods.", 'You will be moments away from shops and boutiques, restaurants, and entertainment on Fillmore and Union Street.', 'Close to Golden Gate Bridge and Marina District; convenient to public transportation and freeways.', 'Building Amenities:', '- Indoor Heated Pool', '- Fitness Center overlooking the bay', '- Management team on site', '- Laundry room on every floor', '- In-building parking*', '3D tours of our amenities;', 'Fitness Center – <URL>', 'Indoor Pool – <URL>', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit <URL> today!', '*Pictures may not be of the actual unit', '*No pets allowed', '*Parking subject to availability and additional fee', 'This unit is a rental unit subject to the San Francisco Rent Ordinance, which limits evictions without just cause, and which states that any waiver by a tenant of their rights under the Rent Ordinance is void as contrary to public policy.']
